title: Subaru's New Rally Car, and New Year - /LAUNCH CONTROL: S03E01
description:
LAUNCH CONTROL IS BACK!!  With a new 2015 Subaru WRX STi, it means Subaru gets an all-new rally car. Go through the development, and see the exciting results.

In this episode, Subarus are in action on different sides of the world. 

Subaru Tecnica International returns to the Nurburgring 24 Hours for redemption after 2014. 

In Shelton, WA, Subaru Rally Team USA tackles the gravel stages of the Olympus Rally. 


Produced by Formula Photographic Inc. with Bowes Media Inc. 

About Subaru Rally Team USA 
Subaru Rally Team USA is managed by Vermont SportsCar and proudly supported by Subaru of America, Inc. Subaru Tecnica International (STI), Method Race Wheels, Royal Purple, DMack Tires, RECARO, PIAA and Race Proven.
tags: 2015 Subaru WRX STi, rally, motorsport, Subaru Rally Team USA
